  <brief_title>Assessment of Stability of Mail-in Capillary Hemoglobin A1c Test Kit</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Stability and Ease of Use of a Mail-in Capillary Blood Hemoglobin A!c Sample Kit</official_title>
  <sponsors>
