  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the stability of capillary HBA1c blood samples
      collected by the participant with this kit and mailed to the laboratory at Children's Mercy
      Hospital.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Participants are given home lab kit for obtaining HbA1c by capillary blood and shipping it to
      Children's Mercy Hospital and Clinics. They will mail in sample before their next visit and
      this result will be compared to the HbA1c performed during this visit.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
